io.appium.java_client.pagefactory

Annotation Type WindowsFindBy


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={FIELD,TYPE})
 @Repeatable(value=WindowsFindBySet.class)
public @interface WindowsFindBy
    Used to mark a field on a Page Object to indicate an alternative mechanism for locating the element or a list of elements. Used in conjunction with PageFactory this allows users to quickly and easily create PageObjects. using Windows automation selectors, accessibility, id, name, class name, tag and xpath
